      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Start here: Step-by Step Youtube Tutorial :star:\n\n[![I Built an Auto Lead Finder AI Agent](https://img.youtube.com/vi/3UwutV1x3mA/sddefault.jpg)](https://youtu.be/3UwutV1x3mA?si=FtH1dNr5dtnOFedD)",
